Eastern Platinum Aims for Resolution of Crocodile River Mine Labor Dispute

-- B y   V i c t o r i a   B a t c h e l o r
-- 
2011-05-12T02:00:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-12/eastern-platinum-aims-for-resolution-of-crocodile-river-mine-labor-dispute.html
Eastern Platinum Ltd. (ELR)  provided an
update on the reported industrial action at the Crocodile River
mine operations. The company said it has “at all times acted in
good faith and within the protocols as set out in the
application for safety protocols and labour relations
legislation” and that it hopes “for a speedy resolution to
this issue.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Victoria Batchelor at 
 vbatchelor@bloomberg.net  